    "Nestled amid the peaks of Mount Lebanon, a place where stunning landscapes meet true Lebanese hospitality. Featuring a direct access to the 80 km Mzaar Ski Domaine, along with a variety of adventure activities in both Summer and Winter. This resort features a heated indoor & outdoor pool, a padel court and one of Lebanon’s leading Spas. The resort also boasts a variety of Food & Beverage venues including Le Refuge Restaurant, where local and international favorites can be savoured.",
    "The Monteverde Hotel is located a 25-minute drive from Beirut and offers elegant rooms with private balconies overlooking the Maten Mountain. It features a garden with a pool and a restaurant. Each air-conditioned unit at the Monteverde has an en-suite bathroom. All of the include a TV with satellite channels. A complimentary buffet breakfast is served every morning at the hotel. The restaurant offer diches from the Lebanese and Mediterranean tradition. The nearby area also has several restaurants and coffee shops. Guests can enjoy the on-site fitness centre or rent a bike to ride in the surroundings. The hotel also offers free parking to guests arriving by car. A water park is just a 5-minute drive away.",
    "Conveniently set in Jounieh's Maameltein district, Madisson Hotel features a spa and indoor pool just one block from Mediterranean Sea shores. It has a fitness centre with sauna and hot tub. Recessed lighting provides a warm feel to the Madisson’s spacious rooms and suites. Each comes with a balcony offering side sea views and a private bathroom with a tub and robes. Guests can enjoy body and beauty treatments at Madisson’s spa or swim in the top-floor swimming pool with panoramic views. There is also a steam room. A buffet-style breakfast is served in the hotel’s restaurant. It also offers Lebanese and international fare for lunch and dinner. For guests’ entertainment, Hotel Madisson offers a karaoke bar. The Madisson is 20 km from Rafic Hariri International Airport and only 3 km from Casino du Liban. The Statue of Our Lady of Lebanon at Harissa is a 15-minute drive away. Free on-site parking is available.",
    "The 4 star hotel is within 11 km from the city of Byblos, the oldest inhabited city in the world, where guests can enjoy family-friendly activities, also the famous Jeitta Grotto is 10 km away. The hotel boasts an outdoor swimming pool where guests can enjoy a drink at the bar. All air conditioned rooms feature a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, safe Box, hairdryers and minibar. Private bathrooms are also available in all the rooms. The superior rooms offer from its seating area a relaxing view overlooking the Mediterranean Sea. Whereas the suites include a spa bath with bathrobes and slippers A variety of sea food and Lebanese restaurants and cafes is situated within a 10 minutes’ walk from the hotel. The international restaurant offers you the chance to taste both the Mediterranean and Occidental cuisine. All dishes are made from the highest quality cuts of meat and the freshest fruits and vegetables. A 24-hour front desk at the property offers car rentals and airport shuttles. Ibiza Hotel is situated in Tabarja, Jounieh, 1 km from the famous Casino Du Liban, 3.5 km from Jounieh center and Fouad Chehab Stadium and 33 Km from the Beirut Int’l Airport.",
