    "When you stay at Faraya Village Club in Faraya, you'll be within a 5-minute drive of Faraya Mzaar Kfardebian. Featured amenities include express check-in, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Event facilities at this aparthotel consist of a conference center and a meeting room. Guests may use a roundtrip airport shuttle for a surcharge, and free self parking is available onsite.",
    "Offering a barbecue and views of the mountain, Mresty Guest House is located in El Chouf, 60 km from Beirut. Some rooms have a seating area for your convenience. A terrace or balcony are featured in certain rooms. All rooms have a private bathroom. For your comfort, you will find slippers and free toiletries. There is a shared lounge at the property. Beit El dine is 18 km from Mresty Guest House, while Barouk Cedar Reserve is 10 km away. Rafic Hariri Airport is 50 km from the property.",
    "Set in Batroûn, 18 km from Byblos Archeological Site, Domaine des Oliviers offers accommodation with an infinity pool, free private parking, a garden and a bar. The property is around 31 km from Casino du Liban, 41 km from Our Lady of Lebanon and 45 km from Jeita Grotto. The guest house features family rooms. At the guest house, the rooms have a wardrobe. All rooms are equipped with a kettle, a flat-screen TV, a safety deposit box and free WiFi, while some rooms come with a terrace and some have mountain views. The units feature a private bathroom with a hot tub and a hair dryer. Domaine des Oliviers offers a buffet or halal breakfast. At the accommodation guests are welcome to take advantage of a hot tub. Qalaat Saint Gilles is 36 km from Domaine des Oliviers. The nearest airport is Beirut-Rafic Hariri International Airport, 62 km from the guest house.",
