    "Situated in Al Minyah, 11 km from Qalaat Saint Gilles, Aquarius Touristic Resort features accommodation with a seasonal outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a garden and a terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The accommodation provides a concierge service, luggage storage space and currency exchange for guests. The rooms are fitted with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a fridge, a kettle, a shower, free toiletries and a wardrobe. Rooms include a private bathroom, while certain rooms have a balcony and others also boast a city view. At the hotel the rooms include bed linen and towels. An à la carte, continental or vegetarian breakfast is available each morning at the property. Aquarius Touristic Resort offers a children's playground. The area is popular for fishing, and car hire is available at the accommodation. Tripoli International Expo is 12 km from Aquarius Touristic Resort, while Tripoli Olympic Stadium is 14 km from the property. The nearest airport is Beirut-Rafic Hariri International Airport, 101 km from the hotel.",
    "Batroun van camping, a property with a terrace, is set in Batroûn, 38 km from Casino du Liban, 48 km from Our Lady of Lebanon, as well as 46 km from Afqa Grotto. Located 25 km from Byblos Archeological Site, the property provides a garden and free private parking.",
    "Featuring mountain views, Al-Arja Apartment offers accommodation with balcony, around 26 km from Gemayzeh Street (Rue Gouraud). It is located 29 km from Pigeon Rock, Rawcheh and features a lift. The apartment provides rooms with air conditioning, free private parking and free WiFi. Featuring a well-fitted kitchen with an oven and a microwave, each unit also comes with a safety deposit box, a satellite flat-screen TV, ironing facilities, wardrobe and a seating area with a sofa.",
    "Offering a garden and garden view, La Maison des Sources is set in ‘Ayn Zḩaltā, 37 km from Gemayzeh Street (Rue Gouraud) and 40 km from Pigeon Rock, Rawcheh. There is an on-site restaurant, plus free private parking and free WiFi are available. The guest house features family rooms. The units are equipped with a private bathroom with a shower, while certain rooms here will provide you with a terrace and others also provide guests with mountain views. At the guest house, units include bed linen and towels. There is a coffee shop, bar and lounge. Guests at the guest house will be able to enjoy activities in and around ‘Ayn Zḩaltā, like hiking and walking tours. Place des Martyrs is 37 km from La Maison des Sources, while Place de l'Etoile - Nejmeh Square is 37 km away. The nearest airport is Beirut-Rafic Hariri International, 36 km from the accommodation, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.",
    "Located in the heart of Faraya village, this newly renovated apartment is the ultimate getaway! Just 10 mins drive to Mzaar ski stations! 1 min walk to 24/7 Markets, Gaz station, Bakery, Salon...Free parking available. You may find anything you might need in just a minute drive or 5 mins walk (Pharmacies, restaurants, taxi, police station...). Ramy and his family will ensure that you are safe and have the opportunity to experience the beauty of Faraya.",
    "Situated within 18 km of Byblos Archeological Site and 31 km of Casino du Liban in Jbeil, Beit el Deif features accommodation with seating area. This property offers access to a terrace, free private parking and free WiFi. Boasting family rooms, this property also provides guests with a picnic area.",//270
